column5: Saw this come across my news feed, walking near his front door and ended up with the treble hook of a 13" Jake straight to the foot! ouch haha
Eeek...   I had a smallie put a treble through the side of my finger, under the nail then out the tip..   Dr at Soldiers Memorial told me I should have been fishing barbless, lol.
Wooooow !!!!! Damn that would wake you up in a hurry !!!!!! ........ That's gonna hurt for a while ....
Oh.. my gawd..  That's horrid!!  Better you than your kid though mane...
Ouch... Lot of pain. I saw on youtube how to remove the hook,
Only a Tard would do something like that.
Ya , that's gotta hurt a bit !
Owwww!  That ain't a small hook either
I was never Squamish ...... Until that !!!! Ughhhhhhh
